          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>lengthways into thirds</p><p>Cut your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, then crush your<strong> garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1699439449848-x200.jpg",
