          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> Jamaican-style brown stew free range chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
