            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
